/** 
 * Returns the non interpolated location of this body. Note that the location of en entity should also be available from its LocationComponent. However, the location component contains the interpolated location. This getter retrieves the non interpolated location as calculated in the last simulation step.
 * @param out output parameter to put the location in.
 * @return out, for easy of use.
 */
Vector3f getLocation(Vector3f out);
